Package: vcf2dosage
Title: Polyploid-Aware VCF to Dosage Matrix Conversion for Genomic Selection
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Joash Joshua", "Ayo", , "joash.ayo@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Converts Variant Call Format (VCF) files to numeric allele dosage 
    matrices ready for genomic selection and genome-wide association studies. 
    Handles diploid and polyploid species (tetraploid, hexaploid, and arbitrary 
    ploidy), filters variants by minor allele frequency, missingness, and read 
    depth, and exports dosage matrices in formats compatible with 'rrBLUP', 
    'GWASpoly', 'BGLR', 'sommer', and 'AGHmatrix'. Supports both unphased 
    (0/0/1/1) and phased (0|0|1|1) genotype calls.
